AutoPEP8 2.2.1 (2020/11/15):
    * Update pycodestyle 2.4.0 -> 2.6.0
    * Upgraded autopep8 1.4.0 -> 1.5.4

AutoPEP8 2.2.0 (2018/11/05):
    + Added Djaneiro Python syntax by default (thanks ferrum-salvator).
    * Upgraded pycodestyle 2.3.1 -> 2.4.0
        Details about changes: https://github.com/PyCQA/pycodestyle/blob/2.4.0/CHANGES.txt
    * Upgraded autopep8 1.3.4 -> 1.4.0

AutoPEP8 2.1.0 (2018/02/10):
    * Fixed issue with not passing max-line-length and indent-size to autopep8.
    - Removed list-fixes option.
    + Added hang-closing parameter(disabled by default).
    * Upgraded autopep8 1.3.3 -> 1.3.4
        autopep8 v1.3.4 changes:
            * E226(missing whitespace around arithmetic operator) is ignored by deafult.
                https://github.com/hhatto/autopep8/pull/357
            + Added support of E131(continuation line unaligned for hanging indent) code.
            + Added new option --hang-closing to support alternate logic for E131 fix.
                If enabled: hang closing bracket instead of matching indentation of opening bracket's line.
                https://pycodestyle.readthedocs.io/en/latest/intro.html#example-usage-and-output
            See https://github.com/hhatto/autopep8/issues/339 for more details.

AutoPEP8 2.0.0 (2018/02/04):
    - ST2 is not supported anymore.
    * autopep8 1.2.2 -> 1.3.3
    + Support pep8 local and global configs.

AutoPEP8 1.3.6 (2016/04/13):
    * Disable debug output by default.

AutoPEP8 1.3.5 (2016/04/13):
    * fixed issue with missed argparse package in ST2.
    + added logging

AutoPEP8 1.3.4 (2016/03/27):
    - Removed 'aggressive' option from the configuration.
    * autopep8 1.1 -> 1.2.2
    * pep8 1.5.7 -> 2.3.1

AutoPEP8 1.3.3 (2015/10/27):
    * fix issue with double 'on-save' formatting in ST3.

AutoPEP8 1.3.2 (2015/10/18):
    * fix issue with user config on windows platform.

AutoPEP8 1.3.1 (2015/09/27):
    + new option 'debug' was added

AutoPEP8 1.3 (2015/05/08):
    * autopep8 1.1 -> 1.1.1
    * pep8 1.5.7 -> 1.6.2
    * fixed issue with white spaces in autopep8 option values(#35)
    * fixed grammar in error messages(#34)

AutoPEP8 1.2 (2015/02/01):
    * autopep8 1.0.4 -> 1.1
    * changed sidebar and context menu layout
    * fixed issue with formating in case all tabs are closed(#30)
    * fixed issue with encoding(#31)
    - Option "file_menu_behaviour" was removed

AutoPEP8 1.1.3 (2014/10/12):
    * autopep8 1.0.3 -> 1.0.4

AutoPEP8 1.1.2 (2014/07/01):
    * fixed issue(#28): ignore selected block during autosave process.
    * autopep8 1.0.2 -> 1.0.3

AutoPEP8 1.1.1 (2014/06/25):
    * fixed issue(#27): plugin doesn't work properly in ST2.

AutoPEP8 1.1 (2014/06/10):
    - options "max-threads" and "show_empty_panel" were removed;
    + added new option "indent-size" to specify number of spaces per indent level;
    * option 'show_panel' was renamed to 'show_error_panel';
    * autopep8 -> 1.0.2;
    * pep8 -> 1.5.7;
    * fixed issue with autosave mode;

AutoPEP8 1.0.6 (2013/12/24):
    + added option 'avoid_new_line_in_select_mode' to remove last empty line in select mode

AutoPEP8 1.0.5 (2013/11/17):
    * autopep8 -> 0.9.6
    - "verbose" option was removed from the settings

AutoPEP8 1.0.4 (2013/08/04):
+ different behaviour for right click context menu (issue #22)
    Option "file_menu_behaviour":
        "always": menu appears always, even folder doesn't contain *.py files
        "never":  menu never appears
        "ifneed": default value, menu appears only if path or childs contain *.py file
    Option "file_menu_search_depth" (default 3) define max search depth for "ifneed" mode
* pep8 -> 1.4.6
* autopep8 -> 0.9.2

AutoPEP8 1.0.3 (2013/06/07):
* fix issue with Win7 in ST3

AutoPEP8 1.0:
+ support ST3
+ support per-project settings (https://github.com/wistful/SublimeAutoPEP8/blob/master/Readme.md#per-project-settings)
+ show unfixed errors in the output panel
+ syntax can be provided by settings (`syntax_list` option)
+ use threads to avoid freezing sublime
* fix issue with `format_on_save` option
+ added `aggressive` option
* change default values of `verbose` and `ignore` options

AutoPEP8 0.9.3:
+ support ST3
* change list options in the config

AutoPEP8 0.9.2:
+ Initial support for ST3. (thanks dnatag)
* update pep8.py to version 1.4.6a0
* update autopep8.py to version 0.8.7

AutoPEP8 0.9.1:
* fix conflicts with SublimeLinter plugin

AutoPEP8 0.9:
* use autopep8.py module instead of spawn the process
+ improve speed of formatting

AutoPEP8 0.8:
* fixed issue with exception while removing open file
* update pep8.py to version 1.4.2a0
* update autopep8.py to version 0.8.6

AutoPEP8 0.7:
+ autoformat on save
